snippet.textDisplay:
Lolsy's American accent is astonishingly on point. I literally thought some Floridian had crashed the shoot because I looked away towards the end of the video and heard an entirely unfamiliar voice - and then to look up and realize Lolsy was speaking, I was dumbstruck.


I was thinking while watching this, though...when filming is able to safely resume, I'd like to see a change up in the format with trios on the panel (I almost said threesomes and I knew that was going to be interpreted wrong) - this is mostly because my dream trio of reactors would be Ciara, Justine Stafford and Lolsy, because they seem to span the entire breadth of the spectrum of amusing reactions to things - Lolsy tends to be super effusive and a bit goofy, Justine has realistic reactions with a dry wit (with just enough raunchiness for a comfortable bit of spice) and Ciara is HILARIOUSLY deadpan, no-selling pretty much anything put in front of her...right up until she goes off the rails and starts attacking people, throwing them off chairs and whatnot. They would be the perfect recipe for maximum hilarity, in my opinion.

Hope everyone in the Try Channel family is doing okay and I'm looking forward to when you can get the band back together for more shenanigans!
